leaderboard.explainer.summary = How is the ranking computed?
leaderboard.explainer.body = Rank is an overall <strong>score</strong> that rewards a balance of <strong>labels placed</strong>, <strong>distance explored</strong>, and <strong>label accuracy</strong> — so steady, high-quality mapping counts for more than sheer volume. That''s why the label counts below aren''t in strict order. (The weekly and team boards use the same score.)
